
'''= a peer to peer web search that seeks to make it users anonymous, while simultaneously customizing the returned result based on the individuals preferences'''

URL = http://seeks-project.info

=Description=

Unlike Google your personal information and desires are stored on your computer rather then in a data mining server. The information sent to peers is encrypted making in vary difficult for them to know who you are and what you are searching for. This software is released as a AGPLv3 licensed work. 


